OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and breezy start with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain then becoming dry
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. Remaining dry in
OL,8,Fthe afternoon with good sunny spells
OL,9,Fand light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMainly dry with clear spells
OL,12,Fand light winds leading to a touch of
OL,13,Ffrost. A band of cloud and the odd
OL,14,Fshower will move east for a time
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA cold start to the day with
OL,18,Fa frost for most places. It will
OL,19,Fremain dry with plenty of sunshine but
OL,20,Fperhaps some high cloud spreading east
OL,21,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
