OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and bright on Wednesday but
OL,7,Fcloudier with outbreaks of rain later.
OL,8,FRain bands moving east followed by
OL,9,Fdrier and brighter spells for the rest
OL,10,Fof the week.
